Dalai Lama asks boy to 'SUCK' his TONGUE and Gives WORST APOLOGY EVER
The Dalai Lama has apologised after an unsettling video appeared on social media in which he kissed a young Indian boy on the lips before asking him to 'suck' his tongue. Footage of the uncomfortable incident showed the moment the Tibetan spiritual leader invited the boy on stage during  a charity event at his temple in Dharamshala, India in February. Many viewers online called his actions disgusting and absolutely sick. #DalaiLama #Dark #India
